706690f-a.title: Brooklyn: Sea Breeze Avenue - 5th Street (West)
706690f-a.text:
Sea Breese Ave., between West 5th Street (left)and Ocean Parkway (right),:
looking northeast across Swa Side Park, showing the "Shelter House" at the
horthwest and the Brighton Theatre and the Peoples Bathing Pavilion at the
N.E. corners of Ocean Parkway and Sea Breeze Ave.
August e, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
